  "texts": [
    "Exploring the application of the iSTS concept in various domains, such as healthcare, transportation, and education, is crucial.",
    "This includes conducting case studies to evaluate the effectiveness of iSTS in real-world settings and identifying best practices.",
    "Currently, efforts are underway to apply the iSTS framework in various domains.",
    "For example, cognitive work analysis was used to analyze the sociotechnical environment of human-automation interaction in aircraft cockpits [111].",
    "The concept of human-AI joint cognitive systems was applied to design human-vehicle co-driving [44]."
